    bibo:volume "5339" ;
    dc:creator "Kraus, Fred" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Redescription of Lepidodactylus flaviocularis (Squamata: Gekkonidae), with the description of a new species from Makira Island, Solomon Islands" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313793>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313795>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313797>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313799> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313793>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Portraitsin life of (A) an individualof Lepidodactylus flaviocularis from near the summit of Mt.Austen,Guadalcanal, Solomon Islands; and (B) the holotype of Lepidodactylus makira sp. nov. (KU 350843), Na’ra Village, Naepaepa Mt., Makira Island, Solomon Islands. (A) taken by M. McCoy; (B) by I. Tigulu." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313793/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313795>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. (A) Dorsum, (B) venter, (C) palmar view of left hand, and (D) plantar view of left foot of holotype of Lepidodactylus makira sp. nov. (KU 350843), Na’ra Village, Naepaepa Mt., Makira Island, Solomon Islands. Scale bars are 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313795/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313797>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Map of (A) the Solomon Islands, with (B) Makira Island inset. Red dot is the type locality of Lepidodactylus makira sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313797/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313799>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Location where the holotypeof Lepidodactylus makira sp. nov. was collected, on a ridge in lower-montane rainforest." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313799/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

